snippet.title: Freelancer - Video Game early Trailer (2001) Windows.
snippet.description:
Freelancer- early 2001 Trailer
Developed by Digital Anvil
Published by Microsoft Games Studios in 2003 in March 2003 for Windows.
Trailer is from mid-2001.

Video found on covermount CD of french magazine Génération 4 (issue #147, July 2001)
